# Page Pattern (Portal Admin)

Port từ mobile `VenueDetail`. Reference mỏng: `app/(dashboard)/tournaments/[id]/page.tsx`

```
page.tsx                    # Thin shell: params + permissions + compose sections
  _hooks/useScheduleData.ts
  _hooks/useScheduleActions.ts
  _sections/ScheduleToolbarSection.tsx
```

- Shell chỉ routing params + `PermissionGate` + compose — logic thuần → `lib/tournament/` hoặc `*.derived.ts`
- **Anti-pattern:** god pages `schedule`, `draw`, `registrations`, `moderation` — split `_hooks/` + `_sections/`
- States: `QueryState` + toast — không spinner/error markup duplicate
- Strings từ `lib/strings/` — không hardcode label admin dài
- Max **400 effective lines** — `pnpm size-gate:strict`

```tsx
export default function TournamentSchedulePage({ params }: { params: Promise<{ id: string }> }) {
  const { id } = use(params);
  const data = useScheduleData(id);
  const actions = useScheduleActions(id);
  if (data.loading) return <QueryState loading />;
  if (data.error) return <QueryState error={data.error} onRetry={data.refetch} />;
  return (
    <>
      <ScheduleToolbarSection {...data.toolbar} {...actions} />
      <ScheduleGridSection matches={data.matches} onDrop={actions.handleDrop} />
    </>
  );
}
```
